        "product_description": {
            "value": "ParaLace 550 Paracord Shoelaces are built for adventure and designed to withstand the most rugged outdoor environments. These OD Green 45-inch hiking boot laces are made from durable 550 paracord with a kernmantle design: 9 removable inner nylon strands enclosed by a woven nylon sheath, capped with 4mm black metal aglets to prevent fraying. With a 550lb static load strength and low-stretch nylon fabrication, these laces hold knots securely for fewer adjustments and more comfortable movement. Universally compatible with hiking boots, running shoes, work boots, combat boots and more, they also double as versatile survival gear: build a snare, make a sling, extract fishing line, hang a hammock or secure a shelter. Sold as a pair, these unisex laces are the strong, reliable, weather- and abrasion-resistant shoelaces you'll want to reach for on your next outdoor adventure or work day.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
        },
